   <text:p text:style-name="Title">艹・<text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>草</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>くさ</text:ruby-text></text:ruby><text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>冠</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>かんむり</text:ruby-text></text:ruby></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>rass radical</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Like growing grass. Used by kanjis that has connections with plants.<text:note text:id="ftn1" text:note-class="endnote"><text:note-citation>i</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="Endnote"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://happylilac.net/pdf/2019-poster_5.pdf" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T2">https://happylilac.net/pdf/2019-poster_5.pdf</text:span></text:a>　“<text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>草</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>くさ</text:ruby-text></text:ruby>が<text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>生</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>は</text:ruby-text></text:ruby>えている<text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>様子</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>ようす</text:ruby-text></text:ruby>。<text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>草花</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>くさばな</text:ruby-text></text:ruby>に<text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>関係</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>かんけい</text:ruby-text></text:ruby>した<text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>字</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>じ</text:ruby-text></text:ruby>に<text:ruby text:style-name="Ru1"><text:ruby-base>使</text:ruby-base><text:ruby-text>つか</text:ruby-text></text:ruby>われる。”</text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"/>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2">Example kanjis with this radical</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard"/>
   <table:table table:name="表1" table:style-name="表1">
    <table:table-column table:style-name="表1.A" table:number-columns-repeated="3"/>
